languages.text: "Этот мир был чист, пока твои соплеменники не осквернили его своим присутствием. У Лилэтан нет подобных сил — что-то другое повлияло на твоих сородичей".
"This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."
languages.original_text: "Этот мир был чист, пока твои соплеменники не осквернили его своим присутствием. У Лилэтан нет подобных сил — что-то другое повлияло на твоих сородичей".

traits.locale_text: "No, not at all! This world is pure... was pure... This cannot be — the Lilaethan has no power over your kind, only over her own creations. There must be some other cause which is unknown to me."
"No, not at all! This world is pure... was pure... This cannot be — the Lilaethan has no power over your kind, only over her own creations. There must be some other cause which is unknown to me."
"No, not at all! This world is pure... was pure... This cannot be — the Lilaethan has no power over your kind, only over her own creations. There must be some other cause which is unknown to me."
"This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."

languages.text: “这里曾是个纯净的世界，后来却被你的族人玷污。莉莱赞并没有这样的力量，这肯定是某种其他原因造成的。”
languages.original_text: "This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."

traits.locale_text: “不，一点都不常见！加努斯是个纯净的世界……曾是个纯净的世界……但这不可能，莉莱赞只能影响她自己的造物，无法影响你们。这肯定是某种我不知道的其他原因造成的。”

languages.text: «Este mundo era puro hasta que tu especie lo mancilló con su presencia. El Lilaethan no posee esa clase de poder; debe de haber otras fuerzas en juego».
languages.original_text: "This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."

traits.locale_text: «¡No, en absoluto! Este mundo es puro... o lo era... No puede ser: el Lilaethan no tiene poder sobre los tuyos; solo sobre sus propias creaciones. Tiene que haber otra causa que desconozco».

languages.text: 「この惑星は清らかだった…あなた達種族が現れて汚すまでは。リラエタンはそのような力を持たない。別の勢力が動いているに違いない」
languages.original_text: "This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."

traits.locale_text: 「この惑星は清らかだった…あなた達種族が現れて汚すまでは。リラエタンはそのような力を持たない。別の勢力が動いているに違いない」

languages.text: "Diese Welt war rein, bis Euresgleichen sie mit ihrer Gegenwart besudelte. Die Lileath verfügen nicht über solche Kräfte ... es muss eine andere Macht im Spiel sein."
languages.original_text: "This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."

traits.locale_text: "Nein, überhaupt nicht! Diese Welt ist rein ... war rein ... Das kann nicht sein – Lileath hat keine Macht über die Euren, nur über ihre eigenen Schöpfungen. Es muss einen anderen Grund geben, den ich nicht kenne."

languages.text: « Ce monde était pur, jusqu'à ce que les vôtres le souillent de leur présence. La lilaethan ne possède pas de tels pouvoirs, quelque autre force doit œuvrer dans l'ombre. »
languages.original_text: "This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."

traits.locale_text: « Non, absolument pas ! Ce monde est pur... Il était pur... C'est impossible. La lilaethan n'a aucun pouvoir sur votre espèce, seulement sur ses propres créations. Il doit y avoir une autre cause qui m'est inconnue. »

languages.original_text: "This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."

languages.text: "Bu dünya, senin türün burayı varlığıyla lekelemeden önce saf bir yerdi. Lilaethan bu tip güçlere sahip değildir, sorumlusu başka bir şeyler olmalı."
languages.original_text: "This world was pure, until your kind sullied it with its presence. The Lilaethan does not possess such powers — another force must be at play."
